                "invention-title": [
                    "Wastewater zero discharge device and method for large-scale water electrolysis hydrogen production system",
                    "规模化电解水制氢系统废水零排放装置和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a wastewater zero discharge device and method for a large-scale water electrolysis hydrogen production system, and relates to the technical field of hydrogen production equipment. The hydrogen production system is connected with the cooling tower to form a closed circulating cooling water system, and circulating water firstly radiates heat of air through the fin radiator and then passes through the smooth pipe radiator. The wastewater subjected to suspended matter removal by the ultrafiltration device enters a primary reverse osmosis device and a secondary reverse osmosis device for desalting, clear water generated by the primary reverse osmosis device enters a cooling tower for recycling, and salt-containing concentrated water generated by the secondary reverse osmosis device enters an evaporation system; and the evaporation system is used for carrying out solid-liquid separation on the salt-containing concentrated water output by the secondary reverse osmosis device by adopting an evaporation method. According to the device and the method, water resources can be saved, wastewater discharge can be reduced, the operation cost can be reduced, the cooling water quality of the cooling tower can be improved, and the device and the method have very positive effects on stable operation and economic benefits of a large-scale hydrogen production system."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种规模化电解水制氢系统废水零排放装置和方法，涉及制氢设备技术领域。制氢系统与冷却塔连接形成闭式循环冷却水系统，循环水先通过翅片散热器对空气散热，再通过光滑管散热器。经过超滤装置除悬浮物后的废水进入一级反渗透装置和二级反渗透装置进行除盐，一级反渗透装置产生的清水去往冷却塔再利用，二级反渗透装置产生的含盐浓水去往蒸发系统，蒸发系统采用蒸发的方法对二级反渗透装置输出的含盐的浓水进行固液分离。该装置和方法既能节约水资源、减少废水排放，又能降低运行成本、改善冷却塔冷却水质量，对于大规模制氢系统的稳定运行和经济效益有着非常积极的作用。"
                }
            ]
